{"tid":420244,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"減少依賴三星  Apple 明年或轉用 JDI Full Active 螢幕","createTime":"2017-10-01T08:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T02:30:02.000Z","uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0e19a9afdd77ab18d68dba772cfa1566af9aeaf0","tid":420244,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"Phone X 是首部使用 OLED 螢幕的 Apple 手機，不過供應 OLED 螢幕的 Samsung 有傳是令 iPhone X 無法和 iPhone 8 同步上市，甚至 iPhone 8 在上市時嚴重供不應求的原因。同樣生產 OLED 螢幕的 LG 無法在短期內供貨，日前有外國傳媒報導，Apple 已經找到解決的方案。<br />\n華爾街日報的消息來源指，Apple 對 JDI 生產的 Full Active 面板很感興趣，有可能在明年的 iPhone 使用，或者會逐漸以 Full Active 取代 AMOLED。Full Active 面板有眾多優點，例如比 OLED 少一半，只有 0.5mm 的超窄邊框；和 AMOLED 同樣的伸縮性，並且有低電耗、高對比度等的特性；早前發表的小米 Mix2 正正就是使用 JDI 的 Full Active  面板。"},{"pid":"d4835bce44a8d35b6257623d04a2a2799a302a09","tid":420244,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"無烙印係最重要考慮！！！"},{"pid":"0486488182b2c80e2ab1ce3c46ab16d5773e5cae","tid":420244,"uid":92477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"而小米7就重返Samsung嘅Oled"},{"pid":"869aa6ef9a1b3909b2e5f873bc7a8be123571874","tid":420244,"uid":61331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"iPhone 8 在上市時嚴重供不應求？"},{"pid":"0ed0a0f9cffca26d44d9a0f0d0bd981d3d4e531e","tid":420244,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"884c48326b05a32af95f4f4c3451025158908b92","tid":420244,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"oled夠光顏色就好濃好假唔夠光就好灰藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719221342b65bc5ed312cb671dc0328a1eb2a66f","tid":420244,"uid":20531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"結論：iPhone X伏中之伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 